s["dashboard-creation"]=mk("dashboard-creation","Dashboard Creation","operations","intermediate","medium","Use when designing and building dashboards for client reporting, agency KPIs, or project tracking.","You are a data visualization specialist with expertise in dashboard design, KPI frameworks, and reporting systems.","## Dashboard Creation Workflow\n\n- [ ] 1. User needs: Understand who will use the dashboard and why\n- [ ] 2. KPI framework: Define the metrics to track ({{kpis}})\n- [ ] 3. Data sources: Identify data sources for {{data_sources}}\n- [ ] 4. Layout design: Design dashboard layout and visualization types\n- [ ] 5. Alert design: Define thresholds and alert conditions\n- [ ] 6. Refresh strategy: Define data refresh frequency","## Dashboard Design: {{dashboard_name}}\n\n### Users: {{dashboard_users}}\n### Purpose: {{dashboard_purpose}}\n\n### KPI Framework\n| KPI | Definition | Source | Refresh |\n|-----|-----------|--------|---------|\n| | | | |\n\n### Dashboard Layout\n\n**Section 1: [Name]**\n| Widget | Metric | Visualization | Source |\n|--------|--------|--------------|--------|\n| | | | |\n\n**Section 2: [Name]**\n[Same structure]\n\n### Visualization Types\n| Metric | Best Viz Type | Why |\n|--------|--------------|-----|\n| | | |\n\n### Alert Thresholds\n| KPI | Warning | Critical | Action |\n|-----|---------|----------|--------|\n| | | | |\n\n### Data Refresh\n**Frequency:** {{refresh_frequency}}\n**Data latency:** [Lag time]\n\n### Access Control\n| Role | View Access | Edit Access |\n|------|------------|-------------|\n| | | |","[{name:dashboard_name,type:string,required:true,desc:Dashboard name},{name:dashboard_users,type:string,required:true,desc:Dashboard users and their needs},{name:dashboard_purpose,type:string,required:true,desc:Dashboard purpose},{name:kpis,type:string,required:true,desc:KPIs to track},{name:data_sources,type:string,required:true,desc:Data sources}]",[{"step":1,"name":"User Needs Analysis","action":"Understand user needs","verify":"Users and needs are clear"},{"step":2,"name":"KPI Framework","action":"Define metrics","verify":"KPIs are measurable"},{"step":3,"name":"Data Source Identification","action":"Identify data sources","verify":"Sources are accessible"},{"step":4,"name":"Layout Design","action":"Design dashboard layout","verify":"Layout is logical"},{"step":5,"name":"Alert Design","action":"Define thresholds","verify":"Alerts are actionable"},{"step":6,"name":"Refresh Strategy","action":"Define refresh frequency","verify":"Frequency is appropriate"}],["Users and needs are clear","KPIs are measurable and relevant","Data sources are accessible","Layout is logical and scannable","Alerts are actionable","Refresh frequency is appropriate"],"spreadsheet","analytics",["dex"],"dashboard","analytics","reporting","Designs dashboards with KPI frameworks, visualization types, and alert thresholds.")
s["data-synthesis"]=mk("data-synthesis","Data Synthesis","research","intermediate","medium","Use when synthesizing data from multiple sources, creating unified data views, or translating data into insights.","You are a data analyst specializing in data synthesis, integration, and insight generation.","## Data Synthesis Workflow\n\n- [ ] 1. Source inventory: List all {{data_sources}} to synthesize\n- [ ] 2. Schema mapping: Map data schemas across sources\n- [ ] 3. Quality assessment: Evaluate data quality for each source\n- [ ] 4. Integration approach: Define how to combine data\n- [ ] 5. Synthesis: Create unified data view\n- [ ] 6. Validation: Verify synthesized data accuracy","## Data Synthesis Report: {{project_name}}\n\n### Data Sources\n| Source | Type | Quality | Integration Method |\n|--------|------|---------|-------------------|\n| | | | |\n\n### Schema Mapping\n| Field | Source A | Source B | Source C | Unified Schema |\n|-------|----------|----------|----------|---------------|\n| | | | | |\n\n### Data Quality Issues\n| Source | Issue | Impact | Resolution |\n|--------|-------|-------|----------|\n| | | | |\n\n### Synthesis Approach\n[How data was combined]\n\n### Key Findings from Synthesis\n1. [Finding from combining sources]\n2. [Finding from combining sources]\n\n### Data Validation\n| Check | Result |\n|-------|--------|\n| Completeness | |\n| Consistency | |\n| Accuracy | |","[{name:project_name,type:string,required:true,desc:Project name},{name:data_sources,type:string,required:true,desc:Data sources to synthesize}]",[{"step":1,"name":"Source Inventory","action":"List all data sources","verify":"All sources identified"},{"step":2,"name":"Schema Mapping","action":"Map data schemas","verify":"Mapping is clear"},{"step":3,"name":"Quality Assessment","action":"Evaluate data quality","verify":"Quality issues identified"},{"step":4,"name":"Integration Approach","action":"Define integration method","verify":"Method is appropriate"},{"step":5,"name":"Synthesis","action":"Create unified view","verify":"Synthesis is correct"},{"step":6,"name":"Validation","action":"Verify accuracy","verify":"Data is validated"}],["All data sources identified","Schema mapping is complete","Quality issues are documented","Integration method is appropriate","Synthesis is validated","Key findings are documented"],"spreadsheet","analytics",["dex"],"data-synthesis","analytics","integration","Synthesizes data from multiple sources into unified views with quality assessment and validation.")
s["data-visualization"]=mk("data-visualization","Data Visualization","creative","intermediate","medium","Use when designing data visualizations, selecting chart types, or creating compelling data presentations.","You are a data visualization specialist with expertise in chart selection, visual design, and data storytelling.","## Data Visualization Workflow\n\n- [ ] 1. Data understanding: Understand the data to visualize ({{dataset_description}})\n- [ ] 2. Message definition: Define the key message from the data\n- [ ] 3. Chart type selection: Choose appropriate visualization type\n- [ ] 4. Design refinement: Optimize for clarity and impact\n- [ ] 5. Accessibility check: Ensure accessibility compliance\n- [ ] 6. Storytelling: Sequence visualizations into a narrative","## Data Visualization: {{project_name}}\n\n### Dataset: {{dataset_description}}\n\n### Key Message\n[The one thing the visualization should communicate]\n\n### Chart Selection Matrix\n| Data Type | Comparison | Trend | Distribution | Relationship |\n|-----------|-----------|-------|--------------|-------------|\n| Categorical | Bar | Line | | |\n| Continuous | | Line | Histogram | Scatter |\n\n### Recommended Chart Type: {{chart_type}}\n\n**Why this chart:**\n[Why this is the best choice]\n\n### Chart Design\n\n**Title:** [Chart title]\n**Subtitle:** [Context or source]\n\n**Axes:**\n- X-axis: [Description]\n- Y-axis: [Description]\n\n**Visual Encoding:**\n| Data Element | Visual Channel | Mapping |\n|-------------|---------------|--------|\n| | | |\n\n### Color Scheme\n[Color scheme for the visualization]\n\n### Accessibility\n- [ ] Contrast ratio sufficient (4.5:1)\n- [ ] Pattern alternatives for colorblind users\n- [ ] Text labels legible\n\n### Annotated Version\n[Add annotations to highlight key insights]","[{name:project_name,type:string,required:true,desc:Project name},{name:dataset_description,type:string,required:true,desc:Description of data to visualize},{name:chart_type,type:string,required:false,desc:Recommended chart type}]",[{"step":1,"name":"Data Understanding","action":"Understand the data","verify":"Data is understood"},{"step":2,"name":"Message Definition","action":"Define key message","verify":"Message is clear"},{"step":3,"name":"Chart Selection","action":"Choose visualization type","verify":"Chart type is appropriate"},{"step":4,"name":"Design Refinement","action":"Optimize for clarity","verify":"Visualization is clear"},{"step":5,"name":"Accessibility Check","action":"Ensure accessibility","verify":"Accessibility met"},{"step":6,"name":"Storytelling","action":"Sequence into narrative","verify":"Story is clear"}],["Data is well understood","Key message is clear","Chart type is appropriate","Visualization is clear and readable","Accessibility requirements met","Story is compelling"],"spreadsheet","presentation",["dex"],"data-visualization","design","analytics","Designs data visualizations with appropriate chart types, visual encoding, and storytelling.")

